{"id": 2109, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的完美主义倾向都体现在哪些地方？", "description": "是严于律己型、在乎外界评价型，还是……只对别人要求比较高？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3151, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180105160852pUiraAV09gS3ZIec.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-15T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 259841, "content": "不迟到、哪怕提早两个小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240384}, {"id": 259331, "content": "不知道答案的绝不写在卷子上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238389}, {"id": 259587, "content": "只要自己有一件事真的不好，往后很多年都在声讨自己。要么试图补救要么在遇到相同事情时加倍关切。总体来说是一个不放过自己的后完美主义人格。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239008}, {"id": 259588, "content": "玩游戏的时候以及停车", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153336}, {"id": 340229, "content": "体重。重一两都难受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640401}, {"id": 259590, "content": "绝对不准别人对我的工作成果指手画脚，好心地也不行✋", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239478}, {"id": 259846, "content": "总是想找到更好的方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1240403}, {"id": 259591, "content": "整整齐齐，干干净净", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551106}, {"id": 298504, "content": "自己喜欢做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438327}, {"id": 259336, "content": "做事要么做到自己满意，要么宁可不做", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1101910}, {"id": 259337, "content": "Excel的文字和图片位置要在框内居中", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606621}, {"id": 259593, "content": "必须保持桌面整洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239485}, {"id": 274442, "content": "就是不容许自己一旦开始认真的事有一点点的偏差", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304800}, {"id": 259338, "content": "全屏看视频必须做到只有画面，那些进度条，输入法什么必须想办法屏蔽掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853320}, {"id": 259339, "content": "说做就做", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145011}, {"id": 259340, "content": "排版", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219037}, {"id": 259341, "content": "微薄结尾必须要标点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997383}, {"id": 259342, "content": "只要开始整理东西就要弄得整整齐齐，洗手一定要充很多次水龙头，吃饭一定一块一块的整齐的挖起来吃，走路同样距离步数要一样。我可能是强迫症吧。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236872}, {"id": 259343, "content": "所有的书必须按种类，重要性，大小区分。要不然会很难受，桌子必须是全班最整齐的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237626}, {"id": 259344, "content": "不将就", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117550}, {"id": 264721, "content": "必须达到我满意的程度否则全部重来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1260219}, {"id": 259345, "content": "买东西一定要凑个整。。。。九块我就很难受必须凑个十块", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202782}, {"id": 259346, "content": "书桌桌面必须整洁，每天出门穿的鞋在临出门之前必须鞋底都是干净的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238429}, {"id": 260626, "content": "字体", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1087593}, {"id": 262675, "content": "看剧有几分钟干了些别的事没看仔细一定会退回去", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 259347, "content": "看见喜欢的评论一定要点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213163}, {"id": 262676, "content": "处女座上升双子的我，总想做到任何事情都可以被平衡的好一些。因为害怕做不好，所以任何认真看待的事情哪怕是小事也会提前做好准备功课。啊 真的很累 还容易被人误解", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250284}, {"id": 259348, "content": "撸点甚高", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 259349, "content": "所有不是我做的事上面?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237468}, {"id": 259350, "content": "晾衣服追求轴对称＋平衡", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102270}, {"id": 259351, "content": "这还真难得写啊，随心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853395}, {"id": 259352, "content": "吃饭上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219889}, {"id": 259353, "content": "文章", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174083}, {"id": 259354, "content": "做设计达不到想要的感觉，睡不着觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238472}, {"id": 259610, "content": "必须完成自己想完成的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918502}, {"id": 259355, "content": "了解一个新生行业，不了解透不罢休。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238472}, {"id": 259356, "content": "我就是独一无二的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238479}, {"id": 259357, "content": "聊天也绝不打错别字", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578744}, {"id": 259358, "content": "电脑桌面上什么图标都不能有，每个盘符里的文件都严格命名，不乱放任何一个文件", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183965}, {"id": 259360, "content": "心理洁癖太严重\n别人的不干净不整齐不美观，碰都不想碰，自己的东西再丑再不整齐都觉得最完美，出门在外不喜欢被陌生人碰着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780915}, {"id": 261152, "content": "看别人扫地心痛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1245042}, {"id": 259361, "content": "引号括号的全半角字符类型一定要前后一致", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 265762, "content": "丢了东西就一定要想找到，不然会后悔很久很久", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196341}, {"id": 259362, "content": "东西必须分类，哪怕放的不整齐，也要分类。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113691}, {"id": 259619, "content": "做一切事情，均有顺序，跳一点都受不了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239622}, {"id": 259875, "content": "没什么完美的东西~只是追求更好罢了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164807}, {"id": 259364, "content": "书的边角一定不能折了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236993}, {"id": 261156, "content": "必须百分百准备好才有底气", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165135}, {"id": 259365, "content": "手头这本书看完之后才回去读下一本", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229785}, {"id": 259621, "content": "我的卫生状况(妈妈不在身边时)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239665}]}